column12:
'desc': [u'

Baby Dreams Blossom Soap (100 g) Price: Rs.40

Newborns have soft and tender skin that is easily affected by infections and irritations as they have a very fragile defense system. Hence it is all the more important that mild and skin friendly products should be used on their delicate skin. The Baby Dreams Baby Soap from Morisons is a gentle cleansing aid that can be used for small children. This Blossoms Baby Soap is replete with the goodness of components like honey
column13:
saffron and milk. All of these ingredients together work to give your baby a safe and refreshing bath. The moisturizing properties of milk and honey leave your infant’s skin soft and hydrated.

The antibacterial aspect of the Morisons Baby Dreams Blossom Soap helps in cleansing the skin of bacteria. This mild soap nourishes your tiny tot’s skin with its gentle yet effective formula.
